properties.Name: EventType
properties.Description:
A categorization of events that can occur in conjunction with a party to create a 'history' of pre-defined events.

Ex:   
Individual
- Birth of Child
- Death of Family Member
- Marriage
- Divorce
- Employment
- Loss of employment
- Purchase of home
- Purchase of vehicle
- Purchase of electric vehicle

Legal Entity
- Incorporation
- Reorganization
- Bankruptcy filing
- Annual reports filing
- Audit
